title: VA - Hardcore U Know The Score  -  mp3 320kbs
description:
Various - Hardcore U Know The Score
	


Format:	2 x CD, Mixed
Country:	UK
Released:	2001
Genre:	Electronic
Style:	Hardcore, Breaks

Some top tunes on a well presented double cd pack. Most are oldskool classics, alas they are not in there full 12" form but are shortened or mixed out at around 3"30. The mixing is sketchy and obviously done digitally paying no attention to key changes whilst mixing. But this cd is worth it for the tunes alone!. Should never of been mixed though.
